## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The influence of Christianity on Western culture is a complex and multifaceted subject, and this report provides a broad overview rather than an exhaustive analysis. Additionally, the effectiveness of proposed strategies may vary depending on regional and cultural contexts within the Western world.